api_list.name: Random Wiki - Full Details!
api_list.description: Get you random wiki with: url, header, paragraphs and images!
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://randomize-wiki-url.p.rapidapi.com/randomWikiURL/fullDetails"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "randomize-wiki-url.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
